Step Six: Use the Right Tools to Build and Activate Your ICP
The right technology stack dramatically accelerates ICP development and puts it into action across your sales and marketing programs.

CRM platforms like HubSpot or Salesforce let you consolidate customer account data and better understand buying journeys and lifecycles. For market insights, tools like ZoomInfo, LinkedIn Sales Navigator, and Crunchbase help you find prospect information, from industry to company demographics. For checking a prospect's tech stack, tools like BuiltWith, HG Insights, and 6Sense are useful for analyzing technographics. If you are using an account-based marketing approach, platforms like Demandbase or Terminus help you scale your efforts while keeping tight focus on top accounts. 

